      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm looking at the specs for the Apex industrial drill you sent over. everything looks good but we have a strict requirement for our overnight shifts. can u confirm for me that the battery life actually survives a full 24-hour shift under heavy use? if so, i can probably get the paperwork signed off by end of day.",
