      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That sounds good, but 36 hours is a pretty bold claim for a heavy-duty drill. To be honest, we're pretty cautious about these things because we've been burned before by manufacturers overstating their specs. Can you send over those specific test results you mentioned? I just want to be 100% sure before I tell my boss we're good to go.",
