      "content": "wait, if the info is proprietary, how can you be so certain about the 28 hour mark? if i find out later that the battery actually dies around the 12 or 15 hour mark when we're actually running it, it's going to be huge trouble for both of us. are you absolutely sure there isn't any fine print in the technical manual that says the 24 hour life is only under \"light\" or \"moderate\" use? i need a straight answer here.",
